definition: to put on or wear (glasses, hat, gloves etc)/to respect/to bear/to support
bird/CL:隻|只[zhi1],群[qun2]/(dialect) to pay attention to/(intensifier) damned/goddam

sentences.english: American kinglet with a notable song and in the male a red crown patch.
sentences.chinese: 以歌唱著名的美洲戴菊鸟，其雄鸟有红色头冠。

sentences.english: European kinglet with a black-bordered yellow crown patch.
sentences.chinese: 欧洲戴菊鸟，黄色的头冠上有黑边点缀。
